      • createPeptidDB

        public void createPeptidDB(String dbFile,
                           String outFile,
                           int missedCleavage,
                           int minLength,
                           int maxLength)
        Write a concatenated in-silico database based on the given list of protein databases in FASTA format. Database is saved in multiple files based on first Amino acid of peptide sequence
        Parameters:
        dbFiles - . List of input database files.
        outFile - . The output database files. Add + .XX where XX are 2 first Amino Acids for peptides
        missedCleavage - . Number of missed cleavages in in-silico digest. -1 to bypass the digest.
        minLength - . Minimal size of AA sequences to be recorded.
        maxLength - . Maximal size of AA sequences to be recorded.

      • createTemporaryPeptidDB

        Parameters:

        missedCleavage - . Number of missed cleavages in in-silico digest. -1 to bypass the digest.
        minLength - . Minimal size of AA sequences to be recorded.
        maxLength - . Maximal size of AA sequences to be recorded.
